  <brief_title>Sopran - Omeprazole Treatment Versus Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Omeprazole Versus Anti-reflux Surgery in the Long-term Management of Peptic Esophagitis - a 10 Year Follow up Study of Patients Previously Studied for 5 Years - A Nordic Multicentre Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
